Doctor, do you have the isotopic results...

597
00:23:30,660 --> 00:23:34,960
站那别动
Hold it right there.

598
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:38,030
我不想惹事 好吗?
I don't want any trouble, okay?

599
00:23:38,100 --> 00:23:39,330
该死的蛋在哪?
Where is the damn egg?

600
00:23:39,400 --> 00:23:41,130
我带你去拿
I'll show you.

601
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:43,130
不行 你不能给他
No, you can't give it to him.

602
00:23:43,200 --> 00:23:46,900
我可不想为了一颗化石吃子弹 懂吗?
I'm not taking a bullet for a fossil, all right?

603
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:48,860
跟我来
Follow me.

604
00:23:48,930 --> 00:23:51,600
就在这边
Right through here.

605
00:23:57,930 --> 00:23:59,160
放开我!
Get off of me!

606
00:23:59,230 --> 00:24:01,600
帮我一下
Give me a hand.

607
00:24:01,660 --> 00:24:04,800
不是每个贼都自己带着手铐
Not every thief who brings their own handcuffs.

608
