Holt承认是Forsythe雇佣他
Holt confirmed that Forsythe hired him

610
00:24:18,030 --> 00:24:19,160
来抢化石的
for the fossil heist.

611
00:24:19,230 --> 00:24:20,930
那你怎么还不为了
So why are you not doing

