可以找到恐龙而高兴?
an "about to get the dinosaur" happy dance?

613
00:24:22,700 --> 00:24:25,260
因为他不知道恐龙在哪儿
Because he doesn't know where the dinosaur is located.

614
00:24:25,330 --> 00:24:27,160
如果我们现在逮捕了Forsythe
And if we arrest Forsythe now,

615
00:24:27,230 --> 00:24:29,630
