there's no guarantee we'll get the t-rex back.

616
00:24:29,700 --> 00:24:31,800
我们的证据太过宽泛
And our evidence is largely circumstantial.

617
00:24:31,860 --> 00:24:33,100
需要有力的证据
I want hard proof.

618
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:34,730
- 你想要恐龙  - 我当然想要
- You want the dinosaur.  - Damn right I do.

619
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:37,160
Khatri博士肯定很高兴听到这个
Dr. Khatri will be happy to hear that.

620
00:24:37,230 --> 00:24:38,230
我刚刚从医院回来
Just got off with the hospital.

621
00:24:38,300 --> 00:24:39,730
她没事
She's fine,

622
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:41,300
只是受了点惊吓
just a little shaken up.

623
00:24:41,360 --> 00:24:43,730
我们现在只有一张牌可打
There's only one chip we can play right now.

624
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:44,830
那颗蛋
The egg.

625
00:24:44,900 --> 00:24:46,300
我们可以在上面弄个追踪器
We can plant a tracker on it.

626
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:48,200
我敢说他会把蛋和霸王龙藏在一起
I bet he'll stash it with the t-rex fossils.

627
00:24:48,260 --> 00:24:49,660
跟踪他 然后逮捕
Follow him, make a clean arrest.

628
00:24:49,730 --> 00:24:51,060
我不想用蛋去引诱他
I don't wanna put the egg in play.

629
00:24:51,130 --> 00:24:54,060
太珍贵 也太重要了
It's too valuable, too important.

630
00:24:54,130 --> 00:24:56,060
哦
Oh.

631
