幸运的是
Lucky for us,

632
00:24:57,560 --> 00:25:01,730
我们有人有伪造化石的前科
we know someone with a history of forging fossils.

633
00:25:06,560 --> 00:25:08,230
Khatri博士给了我一些
Dr. Khatri gave me fragments

634
00:25:08,300 --> 00:25:10,530
方解石和沉积岩的碎块
of real calcite shell and sedimentary rock.

635
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:12,800
我要用大理石雕蛋中间的部分
I'll sculpt the core from alabaster.

636
00:25:12,860 --> 00:25:14,260
- 黏合剂呢?  - 已经准备好了
- Adhesives?  - Already mixed.

637
00:25:14,330 --> 00:25:15,800
我们开始吧
We should get started.

638
00:25:15,860 --> 00:25:17,860
我想你不是真要我来吧?
I assume you don't mean the royal we?

