好假设
A correct assumption.

640
00:26:14,760 --> 00:26:16,030
好吧
Oh.

641
00:26:16,100 --> 00:26:19,130
盐酸和碳化钙在一起
The hydrochloric acid is reacting perfectly

642
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:22,060
反应得很好啊
with the calcium carbonate in the shell.

643
00:26:22,130 --> 00:26:24,060
我们做了一个恐龙蛋 Moz
We made a baby dinosaur, Moz.

644
00:26:24,130 --> 00:26:26,430
就像父亲伪造胚胎一样
Ah, like father, like forged embryo.

645
00:26:26,500 --> 00:26:28,030
每个都装上脚铐
Each with his own anklet.

646
00:26:28,100 --> 00:26:29,400
至少Peter跟着这个
At least Peter won't be able

647
00:26:29,460 --> 00:26:31,830
不会找上Rebecca
to follow this tracker to Rebecca.

648
00:26:31,900 --> 00:26:34,800
自从上次倒霉晚餐后 你联系过她吗?
Oh, have you spoken to her since your ill-fated dinner?

649
00:26:34,860 --> 00:26:37,660
我警告过你 Neal
I warned you, Neal.

650
00:26:37,730 --> 00:26:39,100
你 生意 女人
You, business, and women.

651
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:40,700
邪恶铁三角 我知道
Unholy trinity, I get it.

