00:26:40,760 --> 00:26:42,330
你应该感激
Well, you can be grateful

653
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:46,460
猫咪探长没揭穿你的身份
that the Suit didn't expose your agent nom de guerre.

654
00:26:46,530 --> 00:26:48,030
我是很感激
Well, I am.

655
00:26:48,100 --> 00:26:50,100
Peter再深究怎么办?
What happens when Peter digs deeper?

656
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:51,700
会发现法典的事情
Could find out about the codex.

