是啊 或者Hagen
Yeah, or Hagen.

658
00:26:52,760 --> 00:26:54,660
小心点吧
Cause for concern.

659
00:26:54,730 --> 00:26:57,230
记好了 结束才有新的生机
Keep in mind, to make an end is to make a beginning.

660
00:26:57,300 --> 00:26:59,260
你认为我应该跟她结束?
You think I should end it with her?

661
00:26:59,330 --> 00:27:00,860
托马斯·斯特尔那斯·艾略特说的(诺贝尔文学奖获得者)
That was T.S. Eliot.

662
00:27:00,930 --> 00:27:03,660
但如果猫咪探长注意到Rebecca了
But if Rebecca is on big brother's radar,

663
00:27:03,730 --> 00:27:05,430
那就是时候结束了
the timing could be right.

