00:27:11,930 --> 00:27:13,830
偷走彩绘色玻璃窗是很难的
will be difficult with so many witnesses.

668
00:27:13,900 --> 00:27:16,260
是啊 这事情也不急
Well, that's a problem that can wait a day.

669
00:27:16,330 --> 00:27:18,930
确实
Indeed.

670
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:21,160
今天我们重现了白垩纪
Today we revive the cretaceous period.

671
00:27:21,230 --> 00:27:22,600
明天我们去偷也许
Tomorrow we steal a window

672
00:27:22,660 --> 00:27:25,160
和疯子写的书有关联的玻璃窗
that could be connected to a bedlamite's tome.

673
00:27:25,230 --> 00:27:27,230
这就是生活
C'est la vie.

674
00:27:27,300 --> 00:27:29,360
这就是生活
C'est la vie.

675
00:27:31,530 --> 00:27:33,060
不错啊
Not bad.

