00:27:46,900 --> 00:27:48,600
John Mcdowell 和Michael Holt是同伙
John Mcdowell. Accomplice to Michael Holt.

686
00:27:48,660 --> 00:27:49,860
来着送蛋的
Here to deliver the egg

687
