00:27:53,600 --> 00:27:55,160
他安排了和Forsythe见面
when he called Forsythe to set up the meeting.

691
00:27:55,230 --> 00:27:57,630
我们会一直监听你
We'll have ears on you the whole time.

692
00:27:57,700 --> 00:28:01,460
带着这样一件赝品 肯定不会有问题
With a forgery like this, you should be out quickly.

693
00:28:01,530 --> 00:28:03,860
带着五百万啊
With 1/2 million in cash.

694
00:28:03,930 --> 00:28:06,360
联邦调查局在调查Holt?
The FBI is investigating Holt?

695
00:28:06,430 --> 00:28:07,960
我该担心吗?
Should I worry?

696
00:28:08,030 --> 00:28:10,000
不用 只是一个探员
Nah, it's just one agent shaking every tree he can find

697
00:28:10,060 --> 00:28:11,260
遍地撒网而已
to see what falls out.

698
00:28:11,330 --> 00:28:12,560
他没有任何证据
He doesn't have anything.

699
00:28:12,630 --> 00:28:15,830
但是为了安全起见 我代替Holt来
But to be safe, I'm here instead of Holt.

700
00:28:15,900 --> 00:28:18,300
如果你不想要蛋的话
Hey, if you don't want the egg anymore,

701
00:28:18,360 --> 00:28:19,800
我可以转卖给别人
I'm sure I can unload it somewhere else.

