你太着急了
You're getting ahead of yourself.

708
00:28:46,060 --> 00:28:48,130
我需要鉴定一下
I need to authenticate it first.

709
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:50,060
那就快点把
Let's get a move on.

710
00:28:52,230 --> 00:28:53,860
抓紧时间
Ticktock.

711
00:29:05,060 --> 00:29:07,760
方解石含量和卵石纹路看上去是对的
Calcite levels and pebble texture appear appropriate.

712
00:29:07,830 --> 00:29:08,900
我想这是好消息
I assume that's good news.

713
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:11,330
大大的好消息
Oh, it very much is.

714
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:12,930
我想你这下可以付我钱了吧
Then I think this is the part where you pay me.

715
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:15,430
我会的
I will.

716
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:16,800
等我做最后一项测试
After one last test.

717
00:29:19,730 --> 00:29:21,300
有太多次
Can't tell you how many times

718
