But he will see the tracker.

723
00:29:42,300 --> 00:29:45,030
扫描会进行十分钟
The scan will take about ten minutes.

724
00:29:45,100 --> 00:29:46,800
所以耐心等着
So settle in.

725
00:29:46,860 --> 00:29:49,000
听着 我可不觉得这么件小事要花这么久
Look, I didn't think this was gonna be an all-day thing.

726
00:29:49,060 --> 00:29:50,430
知道吗?
Okay?

727
00:29:50,500 --> 00:29:52,330
你是担心扫描会出问题?
You worried the scan won't work?

728
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:53,760
不 我只是不懂
No, I just don't understand

729
00:29:53,830 --> 00:29:55,100
之前做了那么多测试
what this thing is gonna show you

730
00:29:55,160 --> 00:29:57,060
这玩意还能测出什么新花样
that all the other tests didn't.

731
00:29:57,130 --> 00:30:00,030
能测出里面有什么
It'll show me what's inside.

732
00:30:00,100 --> 00:30:01,800
